block prepend content
	- var top_image = "/img/dining-hall/dining-hall-top.jpg"
	- var page_name = "Dining Hall"
	- var side_image = "/img/dining-hall/dining-hall-side.jpg"

block description
	p
	|The Dining Hall is a bright, heated large area which could be used for a whole host of activities, ranging from formal dining to dance and fitness related sessions. Catering, both formal and informal, can be provided in this area and licenced events could be held.
	br
	|  Free parking is available on site.
	br

